========REQUIERED_PACKAGES============

API based email drivers (for mailgun):
    composer require guzzlehttp/guzzle

AWS s3 storage:
    composer require league/flysystem-aws-s3-v3

Image resizing: 
    composer require intervention/image

Image optimization:
    composer require spatie/image-optimizer
        This package use 2/6 binaries:
            sudo apt-get install jpegoptim / brew install jpegoptim
            sudo apt-get install optipng / brew install optipng

Registration using other resurces
    composer require laravel/socialite

Install npm for easier Vue usage
    npm install

Laravel Scout
    composer require laravel/scout

Algolia for Laravel Scout
    composer require algolia/algoliasearch-client-php:^2.2
    

